1. Category

    id (Primary Key, Auto-Incremented)
    name (String, Unique)
    
2. Product

    id (Primary Key, Auto-Incremented)
    name (String)
    description (String)
    price (Decimal)
    category_id (Foreign Key, References Category.id)

Relationship:

A one-to-many relationship exists between Category and Product. One Category can have many Products, but a Product can belong to only one Category.